# Monorepo

- Apps live in `apps/`: `site` (marketing), `web` (painel cliente), `office`, `webhook`
- Use `@whasap/ui` for shadcn components, `@whasap/orpc/web` ou `/office` para contratos, `@whasap/db` for database
- ORPC: `@whasap/api-web` (painel cliente) e `@whasap/api-office` (admin); utilitários em `@whasap/api-core`
- `web` e `office` têm APIs ORPC separadas — não compartilhar handlers entre painéis
- Domain logic (WhatsApp UI) stays in `apps/web`, not in shared packages
- Marketing pages stay in `apps/site` only — not in `apps/web`
- Run `bun install` from root; use `bun run dev` via turbo
- Migrations Drizzle (`db:generate`, `db:migrate`) são exclusivas do desenvolvedor — o agente nunca executa nem gera SQL
